## 🧰 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React.js, Tailwind CSS *(if used)*
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB with Mongoose
- **Authentication:** JWT
- **Hosting:** Firebase (Frontend), Render (Backend/API)

